Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright. On the first hole{\i0}\N{\i1}I can gauge my condition{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while avoiding using up{\i0}\N{\i1}too much energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like an approach shot.{\i0}\N{\i1}No, more like a super long putt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura is always on point!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like it's 253 yards to the edge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A spoon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she's going to try for two shots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be responsible\Nfor making your own dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki is fired up from what{\i0}\N{\i1}I told her before we started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can sense the momentum{\i0}\N{\i1}in her practice swings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's going to use her{\i0}\N{\i1}full power from the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:00:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A 253 yard shot would come up just short.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She can't hit it that far.{\i0}\N{\i1}If that's the case,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she'll aim to drop on the fairway{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and hope that the ball rolls onto the{\i0}\N{\i1}green. That's what she's planning{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little farther left\Nand it would have been perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What have I done? It won't be easy{\i0}\N{\i1}getting out of that bunker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She used some energy for this one,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she'll use even more{\i0}\N{\i1}for the next shot, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. They're already about 210 yards\Naway from the green edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For her first and second shots,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She chose simple shots{\i0}\N{\i1}that would allow her to preserve energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No-pressure shots that would{\i0}\N{\i1}take her 240 yards in two turns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is my ball ahead?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine went just a bit farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't make the eagle. But I still have a{\i0}\N{\i1}a chance to make the birdie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Knowing that I'm guaranteed par at worst,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm going to get that birdie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it my turn yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've made it this far.{\i0}\N{\i1}I can send the ball to the green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to aim near the pin to make the{\i0}\N{\i1}eagle. But I have to avoid the bunker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get the birdie,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she'll aim for the center{\i0}\N{\i1}left of the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll take it in two strokes.{\i0}\N{\i1}She might even get it in one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could also get an eagle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I'd do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Most players don't celebrate{\i0}\N{\i1}when their opponent makes a good shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I'm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what\NTonbo might do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching her golf is just like\Nplaying with a Jack-in-the-box!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use Tsubura for this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This club. I named it Tsubura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the club I gave her, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's aiming to the left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell what she's trying{\i0}\N{\i1}to do with that stance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It could go either right or left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How will she hit it? Where will it go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ladybug!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan on hitting it from there?\NYou can try again, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I might hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way she plays golf{\i0}\N{\i1}reminds me of a little child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,26, 27, 28
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It rolled a little farther than expected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}72 yards to the edge and 79 to the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll use this and aim right for the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl is clever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's been aiming for this{\i0}\N{\i1}third shot position since her tee shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing standing{\i0}\N{\i1}between her and the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was able to set herself up{\i0}\N{\i1}for this position perfectly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And also,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can sense how that her shoulder{\i0}\N{\i1}movements are on point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop jumping around like a bunny!\NYou're distracting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to see where my ball is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. You're funny, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just around 80 yards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could land it right at the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if she's thinking{\i0}\N{\i1}about her fourth shot,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll aim for the area that leaves a{\i0}\N{\i1}straight putt on the final stretch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A gimme.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A gimme dead in the center!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Way to go, Tsubura!\NTake the birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was able to line up a birdie{\i0}\N{\i1}while preserving her mental stamina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she hopes to line up with the pin{\i0}\N{\i1}she'll aim for the green edge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That doesn't leave{\i0}\N{\i1}much room between the bunker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she comes up short,{\i0}\N{\i1}it'll go in the bunker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it goes in, she'll get a bogey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She knows better than to{\i0}\N{\i1}aim for the green edge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's going for it.{\i0}\N{\i1}She'll lob the ball right to the edge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo isn't thinking{\i0}\N{\i1}about her score at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She only has the excitement of the shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She squared up the club face?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lining the ball to the right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ball's lost its power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! A sprinkler? I didn't notice it\Nhidden behind the grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball landed right\Nwhere I was aiming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really was aiming there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe she{\i0}\N{\i1}aimed for such a tricky spot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No professional player would ever risk{\i0}\N{\i1}doing something like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too risky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo's greatest strength{\i0}\N{\i1}is her fearlessness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's also{\i0}\N{\i1}her greatest weakness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't think about her mistakes. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her shot was perfect,{\i0}\N{\i1}but it ended up a failure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be a bogey for Tonbo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki still has a chance for a birdie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she wants to guarantee a birdie,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she'll have to land the ball {\i0}\N{\i1}right on the inside of the green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't want to come up short.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thought of not making it on the green{\i0}\N{\i1} will definitely affect her shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll try to hit it past the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's on the green,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A downhill slice line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} They're probably thinking {\i0}\N{\i1}this putt won't be easy to make.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to enter the bunker\Nfrom the lowest point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure gets yelled at a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She won't be making anymore shots that{\i0}\N{\i1}would risk getting in the bunker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's reached her limit already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her fingers are almost touching the shaft!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That hand rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That stance is ...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shot she showed me on Hinoshima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. The ball stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bunkers on Hinoshima{\i0}\N{\i1}have steeper slopes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was good at steep slopes near the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She also had a following wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She tried the same thing here{\i0}\N{\i1}and the ball stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It breaks more at the end than I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. Hinoki didn't overshoot. {\i0}\N{\i1}She was trying to hit it that far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she overshoots it will land{\i0}\N{\i1}in line with my first putt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what she was aiming for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now's my chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought she was a goodie two shoes who{\i0}\N{\i1}did whatever her dad says. Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't she a clever one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She seems to have experience in competing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a birdie! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is so good! What a group!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been an hour. They'll be on the fifth\Nhole soon. That's close to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Mr. Otoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to see how Hinoki's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is allowed on the course\Nbesides the players.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A birdie on one, two and four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I have to keep my honor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I got a little too heated up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's already at three under.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a beautiful swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Hinoki's swing is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Perfectly straight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful swing makes a beautiful shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of golfer I wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the path that I travelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ema is currently at four under.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After getting one bogey, she got a double{\i0}\N{\i1}bogey on the third hole{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her score has dropped by three,{\i0}\N{\i1}putting her at two under.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ema?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens whenever I hear a big splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, all sorts of\Nscary creatures live in the swamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's probably why\NI react that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, alligators?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After I won the World Junior Open...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...it took me ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We moved to Japan for my father's job,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was finally able to compete again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do all that just for golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After an injury like that, after being so\Nscared. Even walking must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There was someone on the island\Nwho had scars just like Ema's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was attacked by a shark while fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he's still fishing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Isn't he scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he is, but he\Nloves fishing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The love overcomes the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If something were to take \Ngolf away from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do my best to be able to play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my ability to swing and\Nmake shots as beautiful as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it hasn't been all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to be able to play at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that I'm able to play golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that might be\Nmy greatest strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's playing golf{\i0}\N{\i1}because they like it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I feel the same way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Hinoki she's got to\Ntake the top ranking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get out and\Nencourage her to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so determined to\Nmake Hinoki number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I would go around peeking\Nunderneath vending machines
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to find spare change \Nthat people had dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got down on my hands and knees\Nand looked for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,People who claim that\Nmoney isn't everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly have never known\N what it's like to be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miserable problem. \NThat's why I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise to take first place \Nand the prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,People like to talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning isn't everything, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who aim for first place\Ncan take the ultimate prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to be a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they know they can't do it,\Nthey claim it's the effort that counted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the results that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who show results\Nare the ones who receive praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world of golf, there are players\Nwho lack good sportsmanship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,yet they still gain fans, status,\Nand great wealth through their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! Next is Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there are golfers who adhere to etiquette\Nand have a good attitude, yet never win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are countless golfers like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your path to the pros was\Nclosed off when you got cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then you haven't been able\Nto make any progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,even at my lowest,\NI never stole from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something I'm proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get first place.{\i0}\N{\i1}If I don't get first... my father will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found your ball, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura, what am I supposed to do again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's your fault the ball moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose a stroke and\Nmove it back to where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice birdie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nice birdie.\N-Nice birdie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your score?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Four under.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tied for first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to take first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball moved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's your fault the ball moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose one stroke and put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Why is she so calm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Why can't I be like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grandpa Gon Boat Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Her score is in shambles, but I've never\Nseen a more incredible golfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The waves were crazy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo! Mr. Igarashi is coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he couldn't get a hold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My battery died.\NI forgot to charge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's in Kagoshima now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he should be about two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is he coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He heard you took the top on the first day\Nand wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Two more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I thought she'd be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have tried harder today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hit a 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten strokes off yesterday's score.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have been so happy\Nif I had made the top again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that means he'll\Nbe there tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do my best tomorrow I can make him\Nhappy! Alright! I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?\NYou came to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming, Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sound so distant.\NI know things haven't been easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Tossing and Turning Winds"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me so proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm crying, okay?
